{"tid":608448,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"DIACLONE - FOSTER team","createTime":"2018-03-28T07:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T08:15:29.000Z","uid":37125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a0abba4b72eda1b3d3e498451c7ebbcdfd17b0f1","tid":608448,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T07:10:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/27458997_1608417055905616_1969528669760197292_n.jpg?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=838d634c662413384af4d7ff98cba2ae&amp;oe=5B32E227\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F27458997_1608417055905616_1969528669760197292_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26oh%3D838d634c662413384af4d7ff98cba2ae%26oe%3D5B32E227&h=764cc1a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/DiacloneFosterTeam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDiacloneFosterTeam&d=hkTZ7ysebLic5YBkGO%2FL2NZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=a3acd2de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/DiacloneFosterTeam</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">依個 Facebook page 會以小弟自制嘅 Box Art 嚟講故事.<br />\n故事係關於 DIACLONE  (地球防衛軍)  入面一個叫 FOSTER 嘅小隊, 點樣喺X港以寡敵眾同 WARUDER (幻亂誕) 軍團抗衡. 佢哋嘅目標就係將X港從 WARUDER 帝國手中解放出嚟.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/27369221_1608402462573742_3043585574308512325_o.jpg?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=88f8a7fff582568fa914f44849edbc8c&amp;oe=5B6C748D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F27369221_1608402462573742_3043585574308512325_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26oh%3D88f8a7fff582568fa914f44849edbc8c%26oe%3D5B6C748D&h=db6898cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">故事簡介</span><br />\n203X年，WARUDER 帝國又翻嚟搞鳩地球。自202X年以來，DIACLONE 都 BBQ 咗好耐，係時候又要出動保衛地球。<br />\n<br />\n當 DIACLONE 同 WARUDER 軍團喺世界各地開緊火之際，X港又再次發揮佢嘅世界仔精神，人哋喺出面為自己星球打到&quot;堪堪聲&quot;，佢哋就扮低B，將自己宣佈為中立地區，對地球戰事不干預，不聞不問。WARUDER 軍團終於都打到嚟X國，X國班&quot;領導&quot;知道X港嘅戰略價值唔細，加上眼紅X港成為中立地區之後過得好過俾自己管治嘅時候，於是就同 WARUDER 帝國講數，話X國會自動投降，想俾 WARUDER 帝國統治。而投誠嘅禮物就係X港。世事就係噉，多行不義必自斃。個&quot;自&quot;就係X港嘅自己人，X國。<br />\n<br />\n單眼佬都知如果X港落入咗 WARUDER 手中，戰況會變得更麻煩，更難打。有見及此，DIACLONE 下令喺各部隊入面東拼西湊一隊雜牌小隊出嚟應乎住，收集多啲 intel 先。等鬆動啲嗰陣就會調派支援過去幫拖。依隊雜牌小隊叫做 &quot;FOSTER&quot;，行動代號為&quot;獅奪龍珠&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n==========================================================<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">至於咩係 DIACLONE?</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">DIACLONE 係 Takara 喺1980年推出去嘅約1/60嘅科幻戰爭玩具. DIACLONE 旗下嘅一條 line - Car-Robots, 就係而家大家所熟悉嘅 Transformers 變形金剛. 喺2015年, TakaraTomy 將 DIACLONE Reboot, 用舊有嘅 product 以更現代化, 更精細嘅 design 重新推出. <br />\n<br />\n經過重新 design 後, 新版 DIACLONE 系列入面每一個部件, 只要你諗到佢點用(玩), 就可以用自己嘅想像力, 想點砌就點砌. </span><br />\n<br />\nOfficial site:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.takaratomy.co.jp/products/diaclone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takaratomy.co.jp%2Fproducts%2Fdiaclone%2F&d=hkTZ7ysebLic5YBkGO%2FL2NZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=c9ce4bcb\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.takaratomy.co.jp/products/diaclone/</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3ce0f8f6172ac7471338dbae8a8467eb3f2a2ce9","tid":608448,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T07:34:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae2a3387f11bd65cfb76a6d0da0f15a4b447d4a","tid":608448,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T14:08:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba787c6be20fcd1352d1781acce16079d7b87ec","tid":608448,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T17:40:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f03fb20e4ea95621d74673b4f517ff3153cc61","tid":608448,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco